entries.title: 'There was no safety': Former Bad Boy exec gives shocking insight into Diddy's infamous parties
entries.summary: A former executive at Sean 'Diddy' Combs' record label has spoken out about the scale of the rapper's infamous parties as part of a documentary exploring his alleged debauchery

entries.title: Bet that was awkward! David Lammy has dinner with Donald Trump six years after branding him a 'woman-hating neo-Nazi sympathising sociopath' and a 'tyrant in a toupée'
entries.summary: The tense encounter took place at Trump Tower in New York where the pair were joined by Sir Keir Starmer to discuss the longstanding friendship between the UK and the US.
